1
00:02:10,340 --> 00:02:19,820
Legend of Awakening

2
00:02:19,820 --> 00:02:22,579
Episode 15

3
00:02:23,079 --> 00:02:24,030
If someday

4
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:26,990
I break the Lock,

5
00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:30,370
yet the Power of Awakening is used by them,

6
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:34,510
will my end be the same with theirs?

7
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,190
No.

8
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:40,680
The tradition of Zhaifeng Institute

9
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,210
is that no one falls behind.

10
00:02:42,920 --> 00:02:44,760
I won’t let this kind of things happen

11
00:02:44,760 --> 00:02:47,070
as long as I’m alive.

12
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,340
Believe me,

13
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:51,380
with Zhaifeng Institute,

14
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,950
with our companions,

15
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:55,950
I’ll never shrink back

16
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,670
or be afraid

17
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:01,680
no matter what Shanhai Gang wants to do.

18
00:03:18,160 --> 00:03:19,290
We have little left.

19
00:03:20,079 --> 00:03:21,880
Ice Chrysanthemum Wine is so tasteful

20
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:23,480
and Master likes it very much.

21
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:24,810
Let’s leave this to him.

22
00:03:26,440 --> 00:03:27,310
You know what?

23
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:30,020
I still owe Master a “thanks”.

24
00:03:32,980 --> 00:03:33,579
By the way,

25
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,470
where is Master?

26
00:03:41,440 --> 00:03:42,190
He left.

27
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:45,150
He kept complaining his body

28
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:46,230
ached all over

29
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:49,310
and he said the clinic in Kaifeng cost too much

30
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:51,829
so he wants to rest in Zhaifeng Institute.

31
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:55,420
Did he mention anything else?

32
00:03:58,760 --> 00:03:59,270
He

33
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:03,360
said he would take every piece of
the award from the emperor

34
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:05,710
back to Zhaifeng Institute.

35
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:10,630
Master is indeed Master.

36
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:12,820
You cannot make a crab walk straight.

37
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:16,019
You are really good at talking while eating.

38
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,220
I’m sleepy.

39
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:27,670
I’ll go back to bed.

40
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:38,300
Master Chu Min,

41
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:40,280
you’ve known Master for many years,

42
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:42,010
so you must know about him best.

43
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,790
He is a man of great wisdom.

44
00:04:44,159 --> 00:04:44,960
Master Chu Min

45
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,700
If he’s not from Shanhai Gang,

46
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,230
then who is he?

47
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,790
What is he hiding from me?

48
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:58,710
Please don’t look at me like that.

49
00:04:59,040 --> 00:04:59,909
Like I said,

50
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,370
I know nothing about it.

51
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:04,110
Ask Guo Youdao if you want to know.

52
00:05:04,550 --> 00:05:05,430
Master Chu Min.

53
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:12,270
Fine.

54
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:16,200
We are going to go back to Chenqiao Town anyway.

55
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:19,070
He has nowhere to hide.

56
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,950
Brother, how about Lu Ping?

57
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,380
If he’s really in trouble,

58
00:05:31,840 --> 00:05:34,720
are you planning to go there
and rescue him by yourself?

59
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:36,050
I’m worrying about you!

60
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,510
Who cares about him?

61
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,150
Lu Ping is fine.

62
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,600
He should be in the inn right now.

63
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:42,840
We found the body of Wen Gecheng

64
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:44,150
in the forest.

65
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:48,230
That’s great!

66
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:50,170
Everything is fine.

67
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:53,980
Brother, are you okay?

68
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:55,430
You care about him?

69
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,870
No, I don’t.

70
00:05:59,159 --> 00:06:01,990
I just think he’s someone
who can become my friend.

71
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:05,030
Sometimes,

72
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:07,190
he acts like a rascal,

73
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:10,150
but sometimes he surprises me.

74
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,790
His haters hate him,

75
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,480
while for those who like him,

76
00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:18,910
they can’t help caring about him.

77
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:23,830
I mean Zhao Xifan, Su Tang and Mo Lin.

78
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,510
They all care about him.

79
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:27,310
Okay.

80
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:31,490
Sang’re,

81
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:38,110
have you ever told others

82
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:41,000
that Wen Gecheng is the spy of Shanhai Gang?

83
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,230
No one knows

84
00:06:42,640 --> 00:06:45,170
except for the ones from Zhaifeng Institute.

85
00:06:49,320 --> 00:06:49,850
Brother,

86
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:52,760
I know you regard Wen Gecheng as your soulmate.

87
00:06:53,159 --> 00:06:56,220
Yet this time you opened the door
to a dangerous person.

88
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,630
His Majesty shows good sense.

89
00:06:58,840 --> 00:07:00,560
If you give clear explanations to him,

90
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:01,990
he’ll understand.

91
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,150
What’s more,

92
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:06,400
Lu Ping is the champion of the competition.

93
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:09,530
He must be more suitable to be drafted into Longjie Army.

94
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,440
I’ll now go and try persuading him with you,

95
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:12,030
okay?

96
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:13,520
All right.

97
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:16,030
Do you want to dress up?

98
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:19,150
Sure.

99
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:50,200
You should sleep for a little while.

100
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:52,230
After you wake up,

101
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:54,550
you will find

102
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:58,430
that many things are just like a dream.

103
00:08:12,460 --> 00:08:14,380
[To Wen Gong]

104
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,520
These are the secret letters

105
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:24,250
found in the thatched cottage.

106
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,320
They are all about

107
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:27,110
the activities of Shanhai Gang

108
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,270
in Shuo Country.

109
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:31,850
I’ve investigated the people on the list.

110
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:35,780
I’m afraid they are all spies from Shanhai Gang.

111
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:39,470
Ruin all these.

112
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,840
As for the people on the list,

113
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,720
continue to investigate them in confidence.

114
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:44,320
Remember,

115
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:45,950
keep it down.

116
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:49,080
His Majesty pushes for a New Deal

117
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:51,360
and supports me to hold the Force Combat Convention

118
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:54,420
for picking up able men and those from humble families.

119
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:55,920
There are many officials

120
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:58,580
from distinguished families, like Xia Bojian,

121
00:08:58,680 --> 00:09:00,150
opposing this.

122
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:02,110
If Wen Gecheng

123
00:09:02,280 --> 00:09:03,510
gives them the handle

124
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:05,010
to destroy the New Deal,

125
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:08,290
isn’t is a waste of His Majesty’s efforts?

126
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:11,410
So now we should consider the bigger picture.

127
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,260
Do you understand?

128
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:27,120
Mr. Wen was attacked and killed accidentally

129
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,030
by enemies.

130
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:30,920
I feel deeply sorrowful.

131
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:34,550
I shall take revenge for Mr. Wen by myself.

132
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,310
I hope

133
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:40,240
that this is the end of the story.

134
00:09:40,920 --> 00:09:41,750
I know.

135
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:47,000
Family Qin produces only officials loyal to his sovereign,

136
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:49,110
and it can’t be stained.

137
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:52,610
After I kill all the crafty sycophant,

138
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:55,760
I will go visit His Majesty and ask for punishment.

139
00:09:59,980 --> 00:10:07,860
[To Wen Chu]

140
00:10:07,860 --> 00:10:14,460
[List]

141
00:10:40,020 --> 00:10:47,900
[Zhiwei Thatched Cottage]

142
00:10:54,140 --> 00:10:56,380
[Hongfu Inn]

143
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,920
Mr. Lu, please wait a minute.

144
00:10:58,960 --> 00:10:59,920
Order from General Qin.

145
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:02,240
No one can go out because Shanhai Gang is rising in revolt.

146
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:03,160
There’ll be someone

147
00:11:03,160 --> 00:11:04,760
to take charge of your meals.

148
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:19,510
Brother, why are you back?

149
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:21,710
Have you found

150
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:23,280
that the inn is all empty?

151
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:25,640
And Longjie Amy is monitoring all of us outside.

152
00:11:25,640 --> 00:11:26,800
I think something has gone wrong.

153
00:11:26,800 --> 00:11:29,030
Did we make any mistakes?

154
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:31,290
Everything is supposed to be done.

155
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,870
Is Qin Qi from Shanhai Gang?

156
00:11:36,280 --> 00:11:36,740
Damn it,

157
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:39,150
do you remember

158
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:41,240
how Wen Gecheng became an official?

159
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:42,240
Because of Qin Qi?

160
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:45,010
Exactly.

161
00:11:46,160 --> 00:11:48,490
It’s because of Qin Qi’s recommendation.

162
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:50,190
These years,

163
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:52,180
Wen Gecheng works for Family Qin.

164
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:54,360
So it’s easy to understand that
he cultivates his own people

165
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:56,000
and develops personal relationship in the court.

166
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:58,070
Qin Qi helps a lot.

167
00:11:58,640 --> 00:12:00,800
So if the fact of Wen Gecheng being the spy

168
00:12:00,800 --> 00:12:01,590
is exposed,

169
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:04,310
Qin Qi will be found guilty

170
00:12:04,920 --> 00:12:06,580
even though he knows nothing.

171
00:12:08,560 --> 00:12:09,310
Like I said,

172
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:11,640
no good things happen when I’m with you.

173
00:12:12,040 --> 00:12:12,570
Brother,

174
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:14,400
we’d rather kill a way out

175
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:15,800
than wait for death here.

176
00:12:17,650 --> 00:12:18,280
Who’s there?

177
00:12:18,280 --> 00:12:19,590
Mr. Lu, it’s me.

178
00:12:20,920 --> 00:12:21,520
Miss Ling.

179
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:24,490
I came here in the disguise of a maid-servant.

180
00:12:26,040 --> 00:12:27,100
No time to explain.

181
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,720
I’m afraid General Qin will take actions.

182
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:29,720
Before the troop comes here,

183
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:31,320
everyone, please follow me.

184
00:12:36,350 --> 00:12:37,050
Stop.

185
00:12:40,520 --> 00:12:41,120
Follow me.

186
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:57,780
[Farewell]

187
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:02,590
Cunning you!

188
00:13:03,760 --> 00:13:04,960
Scour the whole city!

189
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:07,040
Order from the General,

190
00:13:07,040 --> 00:13:08,480
no one from Zhaifeng Institute

191
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:09,350
shall be left.

192
00:13:21,280 --> 00:13:22,740
I think no soldier is here.

193
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:23,720
Miss Ling,

194
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:26,680
shouldn’t you be recuperating in Scripture Library?

195
00:13:26,680 --> 00:13:27,610
Why are you here?

196
00:13:27,800 --> 00:13:29,910
Master Chu Min asked me to take you out

197
00:13:30,160 --> 00:13:31,910
for she sensed danger.

198
00:13:32,040 --> 00:13:33,560
It’s because of your courage and observation

199
00:13:33,560 --> 00:13:34,820
that we can be rescued.

200
00:13:35,560 --> 00:13:36,510
I think

201
00:13:36,680 --> 00:13:38,340
she only wants to save Lu Ping.

202
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:39,930
And we benefit from Lu Ping.

203
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:42,070
Mr. Lu,

204
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:44,590
you should go out right now

205
00:13:44,880 --> 00:13:47,210
because the gatekeepers are slackening.

206
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:49,990
It seems that we four

207
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:52,600
are on the way of running for our life.

208
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:53,590
I think

209
00:13:53,720 --> 00:13:56,390
we four are destined to be together forever.

210
00:13:57,040 --> 00:13:59,110
How about we pick up a group title?

211
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:01,080
Then we can at least be referred to

212
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:02,790
in the future.

213
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:04,190
How about

214
00:14:04,640 --> 00:14:07,040
the Ever-Lasting Four Heroes of Zhaifeng.

215
00:14:10,680 --> 00:14:11,680
What do you think?

216
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:12,910
Terrible name!

217
00:14:13,640 --> 00:14:14,390
Why?

218
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:16,050
I think it’s very powerful.

219
00:14:17,560 --> 00:14:19,430
Miss Ling,

220
00:14:19,920 --> 00:14:21,200
do you have any plan in the future?

221
00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:21,710
Right.

222
00:14:22,160 --> 00:14:23,480
You helped us this time.

223
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:25,070
Qin Qi won’t forgive you.

224
00:14:25,880 --> 00:14:27,140
I’ll find a way to live.

225
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:29,530
With such a humble life,

226
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:31,130
I don’t deserve your worry.

227
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:31,990
Miss Ling,

228
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:35,120
you can go to Zhaifeng Institute with us

229
00:14:35,120 --> 00:14:36,630
if you want.

230
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:39,100
You can live a new life!

231
00:14:39,560 --> 00:14:40,110
Can…

232
00:14:41,160 --> 00:14:41,990
Can I?

233
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:43,960
Zhaifeng Institute is a simple place

234
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:45,290
but we live as we please.

235
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:47,470
Miss Ling teaches me

236
00:14:48,160 --> 00:14:50,190
that the hardest part is to let go.

237
00:14:53,160 --> 00:14:55,160
I think we should hurry up going out.

238
00:14:55,680 --> 00:14:56,110
Go!

239
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:13,040
Miss Ling!

240
00:15:13,280 --> 00:15:14,400
-Miss Ling.
-Miss Ling.

241
00:15:14,400 --> 00:15:15,000
Miss Ling!

242
00:15:15,880 --> 00:15:16,630
Miss Ling!

243
00:15:48,920 --> 00:15:50,010
Mr. Lu,

244
00:15:52,180 --> 00:15:56,750
I don’t have the time to live a new life.

245
00:16:01,220 --> 00:16:02,130
Miss Ling!

246
00:16:16,780 --> 00:16:18,290
Why did you kill her?

247
00:16:20,380 --> 00:16:22,130
She’s just a normal lady.

248
00:16:24,300 --> 00:16:25,830
She’s neither your soldier

249
00:16:26,860 --> 00:16:28,090
nor your enemy.

250
00:16:30,020 --> 00:16:32,850
It’s my family affair.

251
00:16:33,860 --> 00:16:35,090
Some people

252
00:16:35,540 --> 00:16:36,810
are meant to die

253
00:16:37,340 --> 00:16:39,270
and they don’t have chance to flee.

254
00:16:40,100 --> 00:16:40,890
Qin Qi,

255
00:16:41,780 --> 00:16:44,420
you confuse right and wrong and kills innocent people.

256
00:16:44,420 --> 00:16:46,700
Do you know what is rule and what is fairness?

257
00:16:46,700 --> 00:16:49,890
You killed important officials,

258
00:16:50,420 --> 00:16:52,300
and do you know what is rule and fairness?

259
00:16:52,300 --> 00:16:52,730
You!

260
00:16:55,040 --> 00:16:55,710
Lu Ping,

261
00:16:56,600 --> 00:16:59,400
I guess you have some relations with Shanhai Gang.

262
00:16:59,560 --> 00:17:00,030
Okay.

263
00:17:00,640 --> 00:17:02,240
I’ll give you another chance.

264
00:17:02,240 --> 00:17:03,950
You come back with me

265
00:17:04,109 --> 00:17:05,480
and help me to investigate.

266
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:07,670
You can be forgiven this time

267
00:17:08,060 --> 00:17:09,310
because you are a friend of Sang’re.

268
00:17:09,310 --> 00:17:09,910
Bah!

269
00:17:10,520 --> 00:17:11,630
What a smell of you!

270
00:17:11,800 --> 00:17:13,819
I can even smell it three li away!

271
00:17:14,400 --> 00:17:16,030
There should be someone

272
00:17:16,359 --> 00:17:18,440
to bear the crime of the Force Combat Convention.

273
00:17:18,440 --> 00:17:20,040
Lu Ping, you can’t trust him.

274
00:17:20,960 --> 00:17:21,910
I’ll go with you,

275
00:17:24,109 --> 00:17:25,440
but you must let them go.

276
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:28,060
I never negotiate.

277
00:17:53,760 --> 00:17:54,430
Su Tang,

278
00:17:58,000 --> 00:17:59,590
I hid for so many years.

279
00:18:02,360 --> 00:18:04,470
Today, I want to fight for Zhaifeng.

280
00:18:06,800 --> 00:18:08,390
Brother, you have my back.

281
00:18:09,640 --> 00:18:10,240
All right.

282
00:18:10,760 --> 00:18:12,510
Fight to death is of much pride.

283
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:14,950
General Qin,

284
00:18:15,880 --> 00:18:16,670
listen!

285
00:18:19,560 --> 00:18:21,560
We Zhaifeng disciples have nothing

286
00:18:23,240 --> 00:18:24,550
but a strong backbone.

287
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:32,470
Okay.

288
00:18:35,760 --> 00:18:36,890
To the Longjie Army.

289
00:18:36,960 --> 00:18:37,550
Yes sir.

290
00:18:38,130 --> 00:18:40,150
Lu Ping killed royal officials,

291
00:18:40,600 --> 00:18:42,530
and he’s meant to die for his crime.

292
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:44,950
Others are his accomplices.

293
00:18:45,440 --> 00:18:46,840
Carry out the execution on the spot.

294
00:18:46,840 --> 00:18:47,390
Yes sir.

295
00:18:58,200 --> 00:18:59,200
Loose the arrows.

296
00:19:33,560 --> 00:19:34,070
Sir,

297
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:36,230
Miss Ling.

298
00:19:36,480 --> 00:19:37,910
You are way too kind.

299
00:19:38,600 --> 00:19:41,440
Why do you care about a dead body when you are in danger?

300
00:19:41,440 --> 00:19:42,920
Do you want to carry the body

301
00:19:42,920 --> 00:19:44,350
when you are on the flee?

302
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:55,280
Why do you always appear at the critical juncture?

303
00:20:00,200 --> 00:20:03,000
Why do you keep rescuing me at the risk of your life?

304
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:07,750
A thief.

305
00:20:09,880 --> 00:20:10,990
Who are you?

306
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:36,630
Don’t you think he’s familiar?

307
00:20:38,160 --> 00:20:39,430
Like a shadow,

308
00:20:40,920 --> 00:20:42,580
he’s watching us all the time.

309
00:20:44,160 --> 00:20:46,400
Now he’s trying to distract Qin Qi for us.

310
00:20:46,400 --> 00:20:48,260
With such profound martial arts,

311
00:20:48,720 --> 00:20:49,980
he knows how to escape.

312
00:20:50,880 --> 00:20:52,120
We can’t stay too long.

313
00:20:52,120 --> 00:20:53,270
We’d better go.

314
00:20:53,600 --> 00:20:55,150
Don’t let him down.

315
00:20:56,360 --> 00:20:57,560
We shall finally meet

316
00:20:58,160 --> 00:21:00,370
if our destinies are meant to be together.

317
00:21:00,370 --> 00:21:01,630
I’ll check the horses.

318
00:21:04,840 --> 00:21:06,670
Brother, where are we going?

319
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:10,070
Qin Qi will try to find us.

320
00:21:10,920 --> 00:21:12,580
The four of us are easy to spot.

321
00:21:13,040 --> 00:21:14,500
We shall not act together.

322
00:21:14,640 --> 00:21:15,970
You go north with Mo Lin,

323
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:17,990
and find a safe place to hide.

324
00:21:18,440 --> 00:21:19,240
How about you?

325
00:21:19,440 --> 00:21:21,470
Are you going to leave me all alone?

326
00:21:21,760 --> 00:21:22,350
Lu Ping,

327
00:21:22,800 --> 00:21:23,840
what are you doing?

328
00:21:23,840 --> 00:21:24,900
She’s your sister.

329
00:21:25,320 --> 00:21:26,360
And now you give her up.

330
00:21:26,360 --> 00:21:27,920
Mo Lin, don’t mess things up.

331
00:21:27,920 --> 00:21:28,790
I won’t go.

332
00:21:29,200 --> 00:21:30,200
Senior once said,

333
00:21:30,320 --> 00:21:33,000
no one in Zhaifeng Institute shall be left behind.

334
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:33,710
Su Tang,

335
00:21:35,600 --> 00:21:37,000
after eating this candy,

336
00:21:37,920 --> 00:21:39,320
you should be a grown-up.

337
00:21:42,320 --> 00:21:42,850
Brother,

338
00:21:43,400 --> 00:21:45,000
I won’t eat candies any more.

339
00:21:45,040 --> 00:21:46,360
You can bring me with you.

340
00:21:46,360 --> 00:21:48,310
I can fight for you and protect you.

341
00:21:48,520 --> 00:21:49,470
You’ve promised

342
00:21:49,520 --> 00:21:50,320
that you’ll always take me

343
00:21:50,320 --> 00:21:51,870
because you saved my life.

344
00:21:52,560 --> 00:21:53,710
In Shanhai Gang,

345
00:21:55,280 --> 00:21:57,140
I would have had no courage to live

346
00:21:57,720 --> 00:21:59,350
if it were not for you.

347
00:22:00,640 --> 00:22:01,970
It is you who rescued me,

348
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:04,430
not the opposite.

349
00:22:05,320 --> 00:22:05,760
Brother.

350
00:22:05,760 --> 00:22:06,490
Listen to me.

351
00:22:07,520 --> 00:22:07,950
Mo Lin,

352
00:22:10,520 --> 00:22:11,780
I give my sister to you.

353
00:22:13,160 --> 00:22:14,760
Please take good care of her.

354
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:17,260
Don’t let anything bad happen to her.

355
00:22:17,680 --> 00:22:18,430
Don’t worry.

356
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:21,750
I swear on the name of No.1 assassin,

357
00:22:22,760 --> 00:22:24,230
that I’ll take care of her.

358
00:22:24,680 --> 00:22:26,830
Okay, deal.

359
00:22:33,400 --> 00:22:33,870
Go.

360
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:39,550
Brother.

361
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:52,330
Where are you going?

362
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:54,530
I want to go back to Zhaifeng

363
00:22:54,680 --> 00:22:56,210
to see how things are going.

364
00:22:56,520 --> 00:22:59,050
If anything’s all right, I’ll go find Su Tang.

365
00:22:59,280 --> 00:23:00,480
It’s such a big world.

366
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:02,760
We can find a place to settle.

367
00:23:03,840 --> 00:23:05,640
It’s exactly what I’m thinking.

368
00:23:06,040 --> 00:23:07,440
How about we go together?

369
00:23:10,200 --> 00:23:11,390
With you by my side,

370
00:23:12,680 --> 00:23:13,810
that would be great.

371
00:23:14,640 --> 00:23:15,640
Of course you are.

372
00:23:16,320 --> 00:23:16,990
Like I said,

373
00:23:17,360 --> 00:23:18,040
no one in Zhaifeng Institute

374
00:23:18,040 --> 00:23:19,390
shall be left behind.

375
00:23:25,760 --> 00:23:26,270
Master,

376
00:23:25,900 --> 00:23:30,580
[Family Wei]

377
00:23:26,680 --> 00:23:28,640
I’m afraid they will soon get some information.

378
00:23:28,640 --> 00:23:30,440
I’ll go packing and take some money

379
00:23:30,440 --> 00:23:32,240
and see you and young master off.

380
00:23:33,000 --> 00:23:33,460
Father,

381
00:23:33,840 --> 00:23:34,790
we are at home.

382
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:36,360
Why are we leaving again?

383
00:23:37,520 --> 00:23:38,560
I heard from Sangsang

384
00:23:38,560 --> 00:23:40,360
that Wen Gecheng works for Shanhai Gang.

385
00:23:40,360 --> 00:23:41,820
But why are we influenced?

386
00:23:42,120 --> 00:23:43,560
Why did you act like you saw a ghost

387
00:23:43,560 --> 00:23:45,220
and come back home overnight?

388
00:23:45,640 --> 00:23:46,390
It’s…

389
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:47,500
What happened?

390
00:23:47,720 --> 00:23:48,050
It’s…

391
00:23:48,060 --> 00:23:48,790
Young mater,

392
00:23:49,520 --> 00:23:51,960
if it you hadn’t leaked out
the identity of Wen Gecheng,

393
00:23:51,960 --> 00:23:53,220
he wouldn’t have died.

394
00:23:54,360 --> 00:23:55,590
Why am I related?

395
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:56,750
Stop.

396
00:23:57,440 --> 00:23:58,590
I have some trouble

397
00:23:58,840 --> 00:24:00,500
and we need to hide for a while.

398
00:24:00,930 --> 00:24:03,590
I won’t let you be hurt.

399
00:24:11,880 --> 00:24:13,270
Shanhai Token?

400
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:28,110
Father, what happened?

401
00:24:28,280 --> 00:24:30,120
-When do you work for Shanhai Gang?
-Stop talking.

402
00:24:30,120 --> 00:24:31,190
What’s the noise?

403
00:24:32,600 --> 00:24:33,350
Be quiet,

404
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:36,000
otherwise I’ll pull out your front teeth
and cut off your tongue.

405
00:24:36,000 --> 00:24:37,260
Please don’t, master.

406
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:38,910
I’ll do

407
00:24:39,560 --> 00:24:40,960
whatever you ask me to do.

408
00:24:41,080 --> 00:24:43,790
I just beg you to let my son go.

409
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:47,120
To fight such a coward

410
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:49,190
smears my own hands.

411
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:52,430
Master sent me here

412
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:54,590
to find Lu Ping.

413
00:24:59,240 --> 00:25:00,870
But

414
00:25:01,240 --> 00:25:03,620
the officials track him down in large scale

415
00:25:03,620 --> 00:25:06,020
which makes it harder for me to take actions.

416
00:25:06,020 --> 00:25:09,690
So Master Wei should help me.

417
00:25:09,900 --> 00:25:10,610
Master,

418
00:25:10,820 --> 00:25:12,690
Lu Ping is on escape

419
00:25:12,900 --> 00:25:15,050
and I’m afraid he won’t cooperate.

420
00:25:19,180 --> 00:25:19,690
Father,

421
00:25:19,940 --> 00:25:22,010
save me, I don’t want to die. Father.

422
00:25:22,380 --> 00:25:23,490
I don’t want to die.

423
00:25:23,660 --> 00:25:24,130
Father.

424
00:25:25,020 --> 00:25:25,650
I’ll go.

425
00:25:25,820 --> 00:25:26,810
I’ll go. I’ll go.

426
00:25:28,020 --> 00:25:29,770
Before tomorrow noon,

427
00:25:30,340 --> 00:25:32,140
I’ll take your son’s front teeth

428
00:25:33,300 --> 00:25:35,210
if you can’t

429
00:25:35,740 --> 00:25:37,610
bring Lu Ping back.

430
00:25:38,060 --> 00:25:38,990
I’ll go. I’ll go.

431
00:25:39,140 --> 00:25:39,930
Deal.

432
00:25:41,180 --> 00:25:42,370
Deal.

433
00:25:54,700 --> 00:25:57,090
When will Senior come back?

434
00:25:58,740 --> 00:26:00,070
You only care about him.

435
00:26:00,620 --> 00:26:02,080
We have the God of Bandits.

436
00:26:02,220 --> 00:26:04,290
Exactly.

437
00:26:04,300 --> 00:26:04,970
I think

438
00:26:05,340 --> 00:26:06,770
they are coming back

439
00:26:06,940 --> 00:26:08,540
on a large sedan chair carried by eight people.

440
00:26:08,540 --> 00:26:09,650
At least,

441
00:26:09,780 --> 00:26:11,820
we Zhaifeng Institute wins the competition.

442
00:26:11,820 --> 00:26:12,480
-Exactly.
-Right.

443
00:26:12,480 --> 00:26:14,010
The champion.

444
00:26:14,060 --> 00:26:14,880
The champion.

445
00:26:14,940 --> 00:26:15,760
Right.

446
00:26:18,860 --> 00:26:20,490
Master,

447
00:26:20,620 --> 00:26:21,740
Shanhai Gang wants no loser.

448
00:26:21,740 --> 00:26:23,270
Even you threaten Zhaifeng

449
00:26:23,300 --> 00:26:24,060
by catching Lu Ping,

450
00:26:24,060 --> 00:26:25,520
his Master won’t let us go.

451
00:26:25,700 --> 00:26:27,300
Or maybe we should fight until the last breath

452
00:26:27,300 --> 00:26:28,340
and we may earn another chance.

453
00:26:28,340 --> 00:26:28,870
Wei Ming,

454
00:26:29,700 --> 00:26:30,660
you’ve been with me for a long time.

455
00:26:30,660 --> 00:26:32,190
I know you are considerate,

456
00:26:32,220 --> 00:26:34,460
but we are not comparable to Shanhai Gang.

457
00:26:34,460 --> 00:26:36,050
Tianqi is the only son of me.

458
00:26:36,220 --> 00:26:37,820
I shall never put him at risk.

459
00:26:38,060 --> 00:26:38,520
Master.

460
00:26:38,540 --> 00:26:39,200
Let’s do it.

461
00:26:41,580 --> 00:26:42,050
Go.

462
00:27:14,020 --> 00:27:15,490
That’s our dinner.

463
00:27:16,780 --> 00:27:19,540
Senior, do you know what is the meaning of fleeing?

464
00:27:19,540 --> 00:27:20,860
We can’t appear during daytime,

465
00:27:20,860 --> 00:27:22,020
we can’t live in the inn,

466
00:27:22,020 --> 00:27:23,370
and we can’t be picky.

467
00:27:24,220 --> 00:27:25,880
The fire is an obvious target.

468
00:27:26,220 --> 00:27:27,420
We are out of town now.

469
00:27:27,540 --> 00:27:29,210
Enemies could be anywhere.

470
00:27:29,980 --> 00:27:31,580
If you don’t even know these,

471
00:27:37,380 --> 00:27:38,440
how did you survive

472
00:27:38,500 --> 00:27:39,610
all these years?

473
00:27:46,940 --> 00:27:48,740
When you fled from Shanhai Gang,

474
00:27:49,220 --> 00:27:51,020
you were caught because of fire.

475
00:27:52,900 --> 00:27:54,360
Don’t mention such thing.

476
00:27:54,740 --> 00:27:56,070
I went to Chenqiao Town.

477
00:27:56,220 --> 00:27:57,690
Qin Qi is not there yet.

478
00:27:58,180 --> 00:27:59,690
So it’s temporarily safe.

479
00:28:00,700 --> 00:28:03,300
Then why don’t we go back to Zhaifeng directly?

480
00:28:05,340 --> 00:28:07,010
We are still

481
00:28:08,220 --> 00:28:09,920
the big heroes winning the Force Combat Convention

482
00:28:09,920 --> 00:28:11,220
in the eyes of Xiaochun, Shitou, etc.

483
00:28:11,220 --> 00:28:12,690
Don’t you want them

484
00:28:12,700 --> 00:28:14,030
to be proud of us longer?

485
00:28:15,780 --> 00:28:17,710
You are afraid of taking them down.

486
00:28:19,540 --> 00:28:20,940
We disciples of Zhaifeng

487
00:28:21,100 --> 00:28:23,160
will never leave compatriots alone.

488
00:28:24,100 --> 00:28:25,630
We rest till the small hours

489
00:28:25,700 --> 00:28:27,210
and we go back.

490
00:28:27,780 --> 00:28:29,220
When we return back to Zhaifeng,

491
00:28:29,220 --> 00:28:31,020
there’ll be someone who can understand us.

492
00:28:31,020 --> 00:28:32,290
Don’t you think

493
00:28:32,460 --> 00:28:34,390
that I’ve gotten you into trouble?

494
00:28:36,180 --> 00:28:38,440
You behave like a son from a noble family,

495
00:28:39,340 --> 00:28:41,290
but now you are exposed to all the dangers with me

496
00:28:41,290 --> 00:28:42,690
braving the wind and dew,

497
00:28:43,180 --> 00:28:44,650
eating only cold food.

498
00:28:52,860 --> 00:28:54,250
I get used to all this.

499
00:28:55,260 --> 00:28:57,210
Lu Ping, believe me,

500
00:28:57,700 --> 00:28:59,450
I’ll find someone to help us.

501
00:29:15,860 --> 00:29:16,330
You!

502
00:29:16,620 --> 00:29:18,150
It’s from Ruyu Restaurant.

503
00:29:18,280 --> 00:29:19,510
I did not steal.

504
00:29:19,920 --> 00:29:21,360
I left Boss Jin with a note.

505
00:29:21,360 --> 00:29:22,950
It’s on Master.

506
00:29:57,700 --> 00:30:00,340
[To Lu Ping]

507
00:30:09,240 --> 00:30:09,830
Lu Ping,

508
00:30:10,120 --> 00:30:12,400
if you want to see your compatriots alive,

509
00:30:12,400 --> 00:30:14,930
come to Zhaifeng Institute alone, right now!

510
00:30:19,300 --> 00:30:19,810
Senior,

511
00:30:21,500 --> 00:30:22,630
it’s time to go back.

512
00:30:39,260 --> 00:30:40,660
Can Master Wei only come up with

513
00:30:40,660 --> 00:30:42,330
such a conventional method?

514
00:30:45,960 --> 00:30:49,950
As for us drifters in Jianghu, death is no big deal,

515
00:30:50,360 --> 00:30:51,960
yet we should try to survive.

516
00:30:52,270 --> 00:30:53,550
You must die

517
00:30:53,920 --> 00:30:55,850
if you fight against Shanhai Gang.

518
00:30:56,080 --> 00:30:57,190
Fighting for life

519
00:30:57,720 --> 00:31:00,120
is better than kneeling down and begging for
mercy in front of evil people.

520
00:31:00,120 --> 00:31:03,440
You and Master Wei are controlled by Shanhai Gang for so many years.

521
00:31:03,440 --> 00:31:05,040
Trusted aids are eliminated when they finish their mission.

522
00:31:05,040 --> 00:31:06,310
Don’t you understand?

523
00:31:07,440 --> 00:31:08,700
You don’t understand.

524
00:31:09,040 --> 00:31:11,370
No one can escape from Shanhai Gang alive.

525
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:13,460
But I’m here alive.

526
00:31:15,400 --> 00:31:16,200
Don’t you see?

527
00:31:18,960 --> 00:31:21,020
Life is in your own hands eventually.

528
00:31:22,040 --> 00:31:24,040
You are free from anybody’s control

529
00:31:24,720 --> 00:31:26,710
if you want.

530
00:31:37,960 --> 00:31:40,560
General, the officials of Chanzhou received
the order of arresting,

531
00:31:40,560 --> 00:31:42,240
and they are searching the town,

532
00:31:42,240 --> 00:31:43,970
but nothing has been found yet.

533
00:31:45,520 --> 00:31:47,380
If it were not for the man in black,

534
00:31:47,720 --> 00:31:49,280
we wouldn’t need to drag so many people

535
00:31:49,280 --> 00:31:50,430
to catch them.

536
00:31:51,930 --> 00:31:53,480
Ask them to pay more attention.

537
00:31:53,480 --> 00:31:54,820
We go to Zhaifeng Institute.

538
00:31:54,820 --> 00:31:56,020
Zhaifeng Institute?

539
00:31:56,480 --> 00:31:57,110
General,

540
00:31:57,280 --> 00:31:59,010
I don’t think they will go back.

541
00:31:59,320 --> 00:32:00,640
They value their brotherhood

542
00:32:00,640 --> 00:32:02,150
more than their own lives.

543
00:32:02,440 --> 00:32:03,680
If anything bad happens,

544
00:32:03,680 --> 00:32:05,010
they surly will go back.

545
00:32:05,240 --> 00:32:08,110
I can see you cherish their talents.

546
00:32:09,400 --> 00:32:11,640
Just that they made hasty movements
without due consideration.

547
00:32:11,640 --> 00:32:13,710
But it’s all late now.

548
00:32:13,920 --> 00:32:15,350
If we lose on Wen Gecheng,

549
00:32:15,840 --> 00:32:17,000
the group of Xia Bojian

550
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:18,060
will fight against

551
00:32:18,080 --> 00:32:19,740
the Force Combat Convention.

552
00:32:20,080 --> 00:32:20,830
Then,

553
00:32:21,200 --> 00:32:23,790
All the Majesty’s efforts will be wasted.

554
00:32:24,320 --> 00:32:25,980
Considering the big picture,

555
00:32:26,320 --> 00:32:27,780
I’ll have to be the bad guy.

556
00:32:29,560 --> 00:32:32,620
I’ll find a chance to ask for His Majesty’s punishment.

557
00:32:39,200 --> 00:32:40,860
General, news from Chanzhou.

558
00:32:40,960 --> 00:32:42,080
Zhao Xifan and his companion have been found

559
00:32:42,080 --> 00:32:43,080
in Chanzhou Town.

560
00:32:43,200 --> 00:32:44,480
They are heading to Family Wei.

561
00:32:44,480 --> 00:32:45,230
Family Wei?

562
00:32:45,760 --> 00:32:46,990
What are they doing?

563
00:32:48,800 --> 00:32:49,630
We’ll ask them

564
00:32:50,400 --> 00:32:51,470
in person.

565
00:32:51,730 --> 00:32:52,330
Go.

566
00:32:53,810 --> 00:32:54,370
Go.

567
00:33:06,100 --> 00:33:09,180
[Zhaifeng Institute]

568
00:33:15,040 --> 00:33:16,240
Lu Ping, it’s Lu Ping.

569
00:33:16,320 --> 00:33:17,180
Lu Ping’s back.

570
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:18,530
It’s Lu Ping, he’s back.

571
00:33:19,090 --> 00:33:21,870
Lu Ping, Lu Ping, Lu Ping.

572
00:33:27,760 --> 00:33:29,690
During my three years in Zhaifeng,

573
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:32,350
I am ready to leave all the time.

574
00:33:33,320 --> 00:33:35,580
But now I kind of feel reluctant to leave.

575
00:33:40,680 --> 00:33:41,410
Don’t worry,

576
00:33:42,320 --> 00:33:44,580
God of the Bandits is here to protect you,

577
00:33:44,720 --> 00:33:46,270
and you’ll all be safe.

578
00:33:49,160 --> 00:33:50,030
Master Wei,

579
00:33:51,040 --> 00:33:52,110
come and talk to me.

580
00:33:52,600 --> 00:33:53,390
Lu Ping.

581
00:33:57,040 --> 00:33:58,390
You finally come back.

582
00:33:59,640 --> 00:34:01,440
I’ve been guessing all the time,

583
00:34:01,560 --> 00:34:03,430
who is the connection

584
00:34:03,440 --> 00:34:05,440
between Shanhai Gang and Chanzhou.

585
00:34:05,640 --> 00:34:06,640
With no surprise,

586
00:34:07,200 --> 00:34:08,179
it’s you.

587
00:34:08,360 --> 00:34:09,889
You know it’s me, then what?

588
00:34:10,080 --> 00:34:11,830
You can’t escape from me today.

589
00:34:13,840 --> 00:34:15,989
How do you plan to deal with me?

590
00:34:16,800 --> 00:34:17,710
Lu Ping, Lu Ping,

591
00:34:17,710 --> 00:34:18,710
don’t listen to him.

592
00:34:18,710 --> 00:34:20,110
Lu Ping, leave.

593
00:34:20,480 --> 00:34:21,179
Leave us alone.

594
00:34:21,179 --> 00:34:22,219
-Go.
-Go.

595
00:34:23,280 --> 00:34:23,750
OK.

596
00:34:24,440 --> 00:34:25,909
Even if you catch me today,

597
00:34:26,960 --> 00:34:29,659
we’ll have Zhang Ping, Li Ping in the future.

598
00:34:30,440 --> 00:34:32,440
If you make a mistake some other day,

599
00:34:32,440 --> 00:34:34,440
do you think you can get away with it?

600
00:34:35,400 --> 00:34:36,699
Get away with it?

601
00:34:37,500 --> 00:34:39,460
Since the day I entered Shanhai Gang,

602
00:34:39,460 --> 00:34:42,060
I’ve never thought about getting away with it.

603
00:34:42,340 --> 00:34:44,489
You are born to be a servant.

604
00:34:45,260 --> 00:34:47,080
They hurt your son like that

605
00:34:47,300 --> 00:34:49,040
and you are still loyal to them?

606
00:34:49,300 --> 00:34:51,929
They arrested my son,

607
00:34:52,090 --> 00:34:53,150
all because of you.

608
00:34:53,320 --> 00:34:54,179
But for you,

609
00:34:54,360 --> 00:34:56,389
my son wouldn't have been involved.

610
00:34:56,600 --> 00:34:58,310
You harmed my son.

611
00:34:58,520 --> 00:34:59,580
If I can’t kill you,

612
00:34:59,840 --> 00:35:01,990
I’ll kill them all.

613
00:35:02,200 --> 00:35:02,830
Wait.

614
00:35:07,080 --> 00:35:10,190
I really appreciate your love to your son.

615
00:35:11,560 --> 00:35:12,890
How about we make a deal?

616
00:35:14,160 --> 00:35:15,230
I give you your son.

617
00:35:15,720 --> 00:35:16,950
You leave Zhaifeng.

618
00:35:28,520 --> 00:35:29,050
General,

619
00:35:29,200 --> 00:35:32,000
why is there someone of Shanhai Gang in Family Wei?

620
00:35:45,640 --> 00:35:46,770
Where have you been?

621
00:35:48,560 --> 00:35:49,350
Xifan,

622
00:35:49,640 --> 00:35:51,840
leave through the back door with the young master.

623
00:35:51,840 --> 00:35:52,700
What about you?

624
00:35:53,140 --> 00:35:54,460
I’ll go to General Qin

625
00:35:54,490 --> 00:35:55,830
and beg for Master.

626
00:35:55,840 --> 00:35:57,060
Why is General Qin here?

627
00:35:57,060 --> 00:35:57,760
Where is Sangsang then?

628
00:35:57,760 --> 00:35:58,360
Take care.

629
00:36:00,120 --> 00:36:01,240
Where are you taking me?

630
00:36:01,240 --> 00:36:02,570
I’m not going anywhere.

631
00:36:06,900 --> 00:36:09,100
[Zhaifeng Institute]

632
00:36:08,200 --> 00:36:10,590
I, Lu Ping, can never be seen through.

633
00:36:11,540 --> 00:36:13,870
Wei Ming and Senior are going to Family Wei

634
00:36:14,340 --> 00:36:15,540
to rescue Wei Tianqi.

635
00:36:16,300 --> 00:36:17,410
Are you crazy?

636
00:36:17,980 --> 00:36:20,010
Zhao Xifan is all alone.

637
00:36:20,220 --> 00:36:21,860
How can he fight Master of Fire Division?

638
00:36:21,860 --> 00:36:23,530
Xifan alone will be at danger.

639
00:36:24,220 --> 00:36:25,950
But if we borrow others’ power,

640
00:36:26,100 --> 00:36:27,250
it’s easier to win.

641
00:36:28,140 --> 00:36:29,400
Borrow others’ power?

642
00:36:29,700 --> 00:36:30,960
Borrow others’ power.

643
00:36:31,340 --> 00:36:32,210
I mean

644
00:36:33,740 --> 00:36:34,610
Longjie Army.

645
00:36:48,420 --> 00:36:48,950
General,

646
00:36:49,700 --> 00:36:51,220
people from Shanhai Gang are all dead.

647
00:36:51,220 --> 00:36:52,880
Zhao Xifan is nowhere to find.

648
00:36:53,100 --> 00:36:55,130
I found the guard in the backyard.

649
00:36:56,140 --> 00:36:56,890
Do you know

650
00:36:57,540 --> 00:37:00,470
it’s such a big crime of colluding with Shanhai Gang?

651
00:37:00,580 --> 00:37:01,640
Please forgive me,

652
00:37:02,020 --> 00:37:04,770
Shanhai Gang threatened me
with the life of our young master.

653
00:37:04,770 --> 00:37:06,600
My master had no choice but to obey.

654
00:37:06,600 --> 00:37:08,530
I would like to tell you everything

655
00:37:08,560 --> 00:37:09,600
about Shanhai Gang,

656
00:37:09,600 --> 00:37:11,030
as an amendment.

657
00:37:12,760 --> 00:37:14,760
You enticed the Longjie Army to here

658
00:37:15,440 --> 00:37:16,550
on purpose.

659
00:37:17,460 --> 00:37:17,850
Yes.

660
00:37:18,980 --> 00:37:20,090
I was forced

661
00:37:20,660 --> 00:37:21,450
to do this.

662
00:37:21,660 --> 00:37:22,290
Asshole.

663
00:37:28,370 --> 00:37:29,530
Lu Ping,

664
00:37:30,140 --> 00:37:32,330
you read my thoughts and set me up.

665
00:37:33,260 --> 00:37:36,170
Our Longjie Army have been manipulated!

666
00:37:47,460 --> 00:37:49,090
Shanhai Gang values Lu Ping

667
00:37:49,180 --> 00:37:50,510
more than I can imagine.

668
00:37:51,620 --> 00:37:53,130
He surly has something.

669
00:37:54,160 --> 00:37:55,430
I must catch him alive.

670
00:37:56,560 --> 00:37:58,030
Leave the guard here.

671
00:37:59,480 --> 00:38:01,940
We go to Zhaifeng Institute as soon as possible.

672
00:38:01,940 --> 00:38:02,820
Watch him closer.

673
00:38:02,820 --> 00:38:03,330
Yes sir.

674
00:38:18,580 --> 00:38:19,210
Lu Ping,

675
00:38:19,740 --> 00:38:21,250
why is my son not back?

676
00:38:21,460 --> 00:38:22,730
What time is it?

677
00:38:23,260 --> 00:38:24,330
Be patient.

678
00:38:25,060 --> 00:38:26,250
Senior will be back.

679
00:38:26,860 --> 00:38:28,890
I wouldn’t have trusted you.

680
00:38:30,260 --> 00:38:31,370
Till now,

681
00:38:31,860 --> 00:38:33,140
you can only choose to trust me.

682
00:38:33,140 --> 00:38:34,290
I can’t wait.

683
00:38:34,500 --> 00:38:35,420
-No.
-Lu Ping.

684
00:38:39,660 --> 00:38:41,010
Master Wei, think twice.

685
00:38:39,900 --> 00:38:41,140
[Zhaifeng Institute]

686
00:38:41,580 --> 00:38:42,210
Father.

687
00:38:42,540 --> 00:38:43,530
Senior is back.

688
00:38:44,460 --> 00:38:45,210
Tianqi.

689
00:38:47,700 --> 00:38:48,250
Tianqi.

690
00:38:48,500 --> 00:38:49,500
Are you all right?

691
00:38:49,540 --> 00:38:50,600
Let me check on you.

692
00:38:51,580 --> 00:38:52,650
I was so worried.

693
00:38:52,660 --> 00:38:53,210
Senior.

694
00:38:53,700 --> 00:38:54,290
Lu Ping, are you okay?

695
00:38:54,290 --> 00:38:55,890
Father, I don’t understand.

696
00:38:56,180 --> 00:38:58,020
Why you cooperate with Shanhai Gang?

697
00:38:58,020 --> 00:38:59,700
Wouldn't it be better if we just stick to our family wealth?

698
00:38:59,700 --> 00:39:00,410
No, I…

699
00:39:00,740 --> 00:39:01,340
Wei Zhong,

700
00:39:01,380 --> 00:39:03,050
you’ve already been exposed.

701
00:39:03,340 --> 00:39:05,290
You worth nothing to Shanhai Gang.

702
00:39:06,050 --> 00:39:07,380
Even if you take Lu Ping back,

703
00:39:07,380 --> 00:39:08,580
they won’t let you go.

704
00:39:08,980 --> 00:39:10,380
Wei Ming, your loyal servant,

705
00:39:10,380 --> 00:39:12,370
has told everything to Qin Qi.

706
00:39:13,220 --> 00:39:15,260
It’s not very late if you stop right now.

707
00:39:15,260 --> 00:39:16,130
Lu Ping,

708
00:39:16,660 --> 00:39:17,810
now I know

709
00:39:18,060 --> 00:39:19,570
why Shanhai Gang

710
00:39:19,620 --> 00:39:20,900
can’t catch you for so many years.

711
00:39:20,900 --> 00:39:21,650
Master Wei,

712
00:39:22,820 --> 00:39:24,230
not everyone lacks the courage

713
00:39:24,230 --> 00:39:25,960
to fight against Shanhai Gang.

714
00:39:27,420 --> 00:39:27,880
Father,

715
00:39:29,100 --> 00:39:30,250
set them free.

716
00:39:30,460 --> 00:39:31,810
Let’s cooperate.

717
00:39:33,300 --> 00:39:34,250
I listen to you.

718
00:39:35,340 --> 00:39:36,140
Set them free.

719
00:39:43,300 --> 00:39:45,330
Senior, Senior, Senior.

720
00:39:45,420 --> 00:39:45,930
Lu Ping.

721
00:39:49,480 --> 00:39:50,280
Listen.

722
00:39:50,820 --> 00:39:53,080
Zhaifeng Institute is dismissed today.

723
00:39:53,440 --> 00:39:54,980
-Everybody go to find your own place to stay.
-Dismissed?

724
00:39:54,980 --> 00:39:55,890
Where can we go?

725
00:39:56,100 --> 00:39:57,250
Yes, how could it be?

726
00:39:57,760 --> 00:39:59,290
I am the criminal right now.

727
00:39:59,840 --> 00:40:01,020
Are you going to be my accomplices?

728
00:40:01,020 --> 00:40:01,750
So what?

729
00:40:01,940 --> 00:40:02,860
You belong to Zhaifeng,

730
00:40:02,860 --> 00:40:04,060
and we have been accomplices for a long time.

731
00:40:04,060 --> 00:40:06,870
Exactly. Yes.

732
00:40:07,220 --> 00:40:08,480
Everyone listen to me.

733
00:40:09,060 --> 00:40:10,260
As long as we are here,

734
00:40:10,980 --> 00:40:12,780
Zhaifeng will not be dismissed.

735
00:40:12,980 --> 00:40:14,010
We shall meet

736
00:40:14,940 --> 00:40:16,470
if destiny wants us to meet.

737
00:40:18,620 --> 00:40:19,170
Tianqi,

738
00:40:19,460 --> 00:40:20,940
I’ll take you to General Qin

739
00:40:20,940 --> 00:40:22,270
to beg him to let us free.

740
00:40:22,420 --> 00:40:22,990
Okay.

741
00:40:31,600 --> 00:40:32,300
Father.

742
00:40:39,020 --> 00:40:39,530
Father.

743
00:40:39,820 --> 00:40:40,370
Run.

744
00:40:40,580 --> 00:40:41,730
-Run!
-Father.

745
00:40:42,740 --> 00:40:43,370
Father.

746
00:40:49,580 --> 00:40:50,690
-Hurry!
-Hurry!

747
00:40:50,700 --> 00:40:51,450
Father.

748
00:40:51,750 --> 00:40:52,440
Go.

749
00:41:28,010 --> 00:41:28,680
Lu Ping.

750
00:41:31,260 --> 00:41:33,140
Everybody go back to the main hall. Hurry.

751
00:41:33,140 --> 00:41:33,770
Father.

752
00:41:33,780 --> 00:41:35,190
Be quick. Be quick.

753
00:41:41,900 --> 00:41:42,500
Watch out!

754
00:41:46,260 --> 00:41:47,660
You go from the backdoor.

755
00:41:47,700 --> 00:41:48,900
I’ll take care of here.

756
00:41:48,900 --> 00:41:49,570
Senior.

757
00:41:49,580 --> 00:41:50,050
Go!

758
00:41:53,700 --> 00:41:54,530
Lay down.

759
00:42:32,200 --> 00:42:33,130
Where is Lu Ping?

760
00:42:33,440 --> 00:42:35,100
He flees to the back mountain.

761
00:42:35,320 --> 00:42:36,780
In front of the real enemy,

762
00:42:37,280 --> 00:42:39,040
could you please offer us a helping hand

763
00:42:39,040 --> 00:42:40,440
without thinking about the previous matters?

764
00:42:40,440 --> 00:42:42,150
Wen Rui, you stay here.

765
00:42:42,360 --> 00:42:43,600
I’ll go to the back mountain.

766
00:42:43,600 --> 00:42:44,070
Yes sir.

767
00:42:44,600 --> 00:42:45,110
Go.

768
00:42:47,080 --> 00:42:48,390
Senior, Senior.

769
00:42:49,440 --> 00:42:50,100
Be careful.

770
00:42:51,360 --> 00:42:52,830
I will take Lu Ping back.

771
00:42:53,320 --> 00:42:55,910
No one in Zhaifeng shall be left behind.

772
00:43:13,520 --> 00:43:15,000
You think I can’t recognize you

773
00:43:15,000 --> 00:43:16,270
if you wear the mask?

774
00:43:16,680 --> 00:43:17,390
Guo Youdao.

